Package org.apache.pulsar.client.api.schema

Interface KeyValueSchema<K,​V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - the type of the Key
    V - the type of the Value.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Schema<KeyValue<K,​V>>
    public interface KeyValueSchema<K,​V>
extends Schema<KeyValue<K,​V>>
    This interface models a Schema that is composed of two parts. A Key and a Value.
